data.title: Wayland New York Zip Code List
data.meta_description: A list of all the zip codes and maps associated with Wayland, NY - Steuben County New York City of Wayland zip code map
data.text: Wayland, NY is a city located in Steuben County, New York and has a land area of 74.87 square miles (193.91 km2). The water area for the city is 0.58 square miles or 1.50 km2. There is one unique zip code in Wayland, New York and it is 14572. The area code(s) for Wayland is 585.
